com.ch_linghu.fanfoudroid.http 中 HttpException 的使用
 

com.ch_linghu.fanfoudroid.http 中 HttpException 的子类
 class HttpAuthException
          NOT AUTHORIZED, HTTP CODE 401
 class HttpRefusedException
          HTTP StatusCode is 403, Server refuse the request
 class HttpRequestException
          HTTP StatusCode is not 200 NOT_MODIFIED: 304 BAD_REQUEST: 400 NOT_FOUND: 404 NOT_ACCEPTABLE: 406
 class HttpServerException
          HTTP StatusCode is not 200 INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR: 500 BAD_GATEWAY: 502 SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE: 503
 class ResponseException
          解析response时出现IOException, JSONException等
